==Translingual==
===Etymology===
based on the generic name ''[[Pinus]]'' (Art 18 ''[[ICBN]]'')

===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''''Pinaceae'''''
#{{botany}} a [[botanical name]] at the rank of [[family]]. [[Circumscription]] and placement of the family varies with [[taxonomic system]] and viewpoint. For the past few decades circumscription has been stable. Placement has been in the [[order]] ''[[Pinales]]'' or ''[[Coniferales]]''.

